Khalil Kain https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Khalil_Kain 0 Khalil Kain (born Khaliloeron Kain; November 22, 1964) an American actor and rapper also known as K. Kain best known for his role as Raheem in 1992's Juice and as Darnell Wilkes on Girlfriends, replacing Flex Alexander.
